      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b001",
      "level": 1,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          198.60000610351562,
          76.5949478149414,
          396.586181640625,
          98.61079406738281
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "区政府常务会议纪要",
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.0
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b002",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          209.52000427246094,
          111.36499786376953,
          385.79998779296875,
          126.99500274658203
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "长府会议纪要〔2025〕2 号",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b003",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          155.18894958496094,
          505.2550048828125,
          171.50579833984375
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "2025 年1 月21 日下午，区长刘平主持召开区政府第96",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b004",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          183.14895629882812,
          185.98757934570312,
          199.46580505371094
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "次常务会议。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b005",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          211.1079559326172,
          505.18804931640625,
          227.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "会议听取区府办关于2025 年区“两会”期间人大代表",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b006",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          239.18894958496094,
          505.19000244140625,
          255.50579833984375
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "建议和政协提案有关情况的汇报。会议指出，各承办单位要",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b007",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          267.1489562988281,
          505.18853759765625,
          283.4658203125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "各司其职，进一步提高办理质量、创新办理方式、完善办理",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b008",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          295.1079406738281,
          505.9090270996094,
          311.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "机制。一是要高度重视，领导带头办理。要提高思想认识，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b009",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          323.18896484375,
          505.18707275390625,
          339.5058288574219
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "把建议提案办理工作作为出政策、做决策、推工作的重要抓",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b010",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          351.1489562988281,
          513.22998046875,
          367.4658203125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "手，认真办好每一件代表建议和政协提案。二是要落实责任，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b011",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          379.1079406738281,
          513.22998046875,
          395.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "形成工作合力。各部门要有大局意识，跨前一步、主动担当，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b012",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          407.18896484375,
          513.22998046875,
          423.5058288574219
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "根据“谁主管、谁主办，谁牵头、谁主办，指定谁、谁主办”",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b013",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          435.1489562988281,
          505.30914306640625,
          451.4658203125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "的分办原则，积极开展办理工作。三是要加强沟通，增强办",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b014",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          463.1079406738281,
          505.30621337890625,
          479.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "理实效。各承办单位要畅通沟通渠道，进一步争取代表和委",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b015",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          491.18896484375,
          505.18853759765625,
          507.5058288574219
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "员的支持理解。四是要强化制度，加强跟踪检查。各承办单",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b016",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          519.14892578125,
          505.18560791015625,
          535.4657592773438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "位要及时把办理工作摆到议事日程，努力把办理工作和日常",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b017",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          547.1079711914062,
          505.30621337890625,
          563.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "业务有机结合，统筹安排、协调推进。要充分发挥年度绩效",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b018",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          575.18896484375,
          505.30914306640625,
          591.5057983398438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "考核对办理工作的激励和促进作用，抓好回访检查、督促落",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b019",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          603.14892578125,
          425.9801940917969,
          619.4657592773438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "实等工作环节，力争让代表满意、让群众满意。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b020",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          631.1079711914062,
          505.1876220703125,
          647.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "会议听取区建设管理委关于编制2025 年长宁区重大建",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b021",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          659.18896484375,
          505.18560791015625,
          675.5057983398438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "设项目清单的情况汇报。会议指出，区建设管理委要发挥好",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b022",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          687.14892578125,
          505.1879577636719,
          703.4657592773438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "牵头统筹作用，做好具体项目的协调推进工作。相关审批单",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b023",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          715.1079711914062,
          505.30767822265625,
          731.4248046875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "位要主动跨前，加快重大建设项目审批流程。相关建设单位",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b024",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          743.18896484375,
          505.1894226074219,
          759.5057983398438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "要落实主体责任，按照分工安排，围绕年度工作目标，全力",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b025",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          80.78894805908203,
          457.8990173339844,
          97.10579681396484
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "推进重大建设项目，助力区域经济社会高质量发展。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b026",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          108.74894714355469,
          505.30621337890625,
          125.0657958984375
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "会议听取区发展改革委关于制订《长宁区聚焦提升企业",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b027",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          136.70794677734375,
          505.1824035644531,
          153.02479553222656
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "感受持续打造国际一流营商环境行动方案》相关情况的汇",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b028",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          164.78895568847656,
          505.30621337890625,
          181.10580444335938
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "报。会议指出，要加强考核结果总结，认真对照测评结果做",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b029",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          192.7489471435547,
          505.30914306640625,
          209.0657958984375
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "好问题分析，加强总结提炼，进一步明确工作举措，争取打",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b030",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          220.70794677734375,
          513.22998046875,
          237.02479553222656
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "造更多特色亮点，切实提升考核成绩。要推动任务尽早落地，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b031",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          248.7889404296875,
          505.30902099609375,
          265.1058044433594
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "主动向上对接，细化《方案》实施路径，加强协调合作，确",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b032",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          276.74896240234375,
          505.30914306640625,
          293.0658264160156
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "保各项任务不折不扣完成。要持续提升企业感受度，紧盯企",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b033",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          304.70794677734375,
          505.30914306640625,
          321.0248107910156
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "业发展的痛点、堵点、难点，持续发挥“三级三系”企业服",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b034",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          332.7889404296875,
          505.30767822265625,
          349.1058044433594
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "务体系作用，有针对性地推出改革创新举措，提升企业获得",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_meeting_001_changning_executive_minutes_b035",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          360.74896240234375,
          185.98757934570312,
          377.0658264160156
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "感和满意度。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
